pageContext.claim: “Pelosi, who, by the way, by the way, by the way, she has totally lost control. She has totally -- it's being run now by this crazy AOC, plus three AOC plus three. Now it's being run by other people, the far left has just grab that party, it is so sad to see.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump tries to suggest some relatively new lawmakers have control of the Democratic caucus, but House Speaker Nancy Pelosi has demonstrated she is perhaps the most powerful speaker in decades, with firm control over her caucus.
